'''Antarctica: The Battle for the Seventh Continent''' is a 2016 book by Doaa Abdel-Motaal is book discussing the complexities of territorial claims on Antarctica and the agreements surrounding the continent.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://graduateinstitute.ch/lang/en/pid/10596/_/events/cies/antarctica-the-battle-for-the-se|title=Antarctica, The Battle for the Seventh Continent, Book Presentation|website=graduateinstitute.ch|access-date=2017-02-28}}</ref> The book critiques the existing treaties and then explores different alternative to find a peaceful resolution to the problems posed by Antarctica's unique situation.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.abc-clio.com/Praeger/product.aspx?pc=A5142C|title=Antarctica|access-date=2017-02-28}}</ref>

